DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260427T190000
UID:260309a5iI_hynKkyR99dhqMbiSw
DESCRIPTION:**Bloomington Expressive Arts Training: BEAT** will present t
 heir 14th annual BEAT Spring Show on Monday\, April 27th at 7pm at the Bus
 kirk Chumley Theater. BEAT is a pre-professional\, community show choir pr
 ogram for children grades 1-12 throughout Bloomington and surrounding area
 s. Come watch the members of Mini Sync\, Syncopation\, Amplitude AND our b
 rand new adult group\, Tempo\, sing and dance their HEARTS out! BEAT invit
 es you to partake in this innovative\, engaging entertainment fit for the 
 whole family!! Come get to know these incredibly talented young people!!!\
 n\nSales start March 4th at noon! Children need a ticket of their own unle
 ss they sit in a parent’s lap the duration of the show. There will be a 
 15 minute intermission.
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/beat-spring-show-april-27-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
