BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:2026 Be More Awards
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260428T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260428T193000
UID:2603096o2XlkZUQ02867x9QqE4Qg
DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Bloomington in celebrating volunteerism at th
 e **2026 Be More Awards**. Presented by the City of Bloomington Volunteer
  Network\, this year’s event will once again honor individuals and group
 s who have made a lasting\, positive impact on the Bloomington and Monroe 
 County community through years of dedicated volunteer service.\n\nAwards w
 ill be presented across eight (8) categories\, including a Lifetime Achiev
 ement Award (Be More Dedicated)\, Volunteer of the Year (Be More Impactful
 )\, and a Youth Volunteer Award (Be More Energized). Each recipient will b
 e honored with an award and a $1\,000.00 grant award to the primary organi
 zation they volunteer for.\n\nThe Bloomington Volunteer Network will also 
 celebrate the City’s progress towards the goal of logging 100\,000 volun
 teer hours in 2026.\n\nLearn more at **www.bloomingtonvolunteernetwork.or
 g/bemore** . This event is free and open to the public.\n\n**This event is
  free!** No tickets are needed for entry.
LOCATION:Buskirk Chumley Theater
URL:https://buskirkchumley.org/events/2026-be-more-awards-april-28-2026/
X-SOURCE:Limestone Post
END:VEVENT
