DESCRIPTION:Tiles & Tastings at Oliver Winery An Evening of American Mahjo
 ng hosted by Mahj in Bloom Mahjong\, wine\, and a little friendly competit
 ion? Yes please. Join us at Oliver Winery for a lively night of tiles\, la
 ughs\, and just enough competitive energy to keep things interesting. ️ 
 TICKETS & PRICING $40 per person — spots are limited\, grab yours early!
  Includes one complimentary glass of Oliver wine \\(non-alcoholic options 
 available\\) HOW THE EVENING FLOWS ✔️ Quick strategy session around th
 e 2026 NMJL card ✔️ Round 1 of open play ✔️ Short break — refres
 h your drink\, switch tables\, meet fellow Mahjong lovers ✔️ Round 2 o
 f open play ✔️ Prizes\, surprises & a special raffle to close out the 
 night EXPECT A FEW FUN SURPRISES We'll celebrate the first Mahjong of the 
 night\, hand out playful prizes\, and raffle off something special before 
 the evening wraps.  PLEASE NOTE This is not a beginner's lesson. Newer pla
 yers are welcome but should already know the basics of American Mahjong. A
 ll guests should bring their own 2026 NMJL card. WHERE Oliver Winery 200 E
  Winery Road\, Bloomington\, IN 47404 WHEN May 15 | 6pm – 8pm
LOCATION:SCERA
