DESCRIPTION:Mothra\, 1961\, directed by Ishiro Honda will show at the Busk
 irk Chumley Theater on June12th 2026\, for the first time in its original\
 , unedited Japanese version.\n\nJune 13th 2026\, will show kaiju films all
  day\, featuring Mothra\, in their original\, unedited version\, straight 
 form the Toho Archives.
